## Code of Conduct

We expect all contributors to abide by our [Code of Conduct](CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md). Please ensure that your behavior is respectful and professional in all interactions.

---

Thank you for contributing to the Virtual Chemistry Lab Manual! Your participation helps us build a valuable educational resource that empowers learners around the world.
